Wegagen Bank is a bank in Ethiopia established in 1997. According to its website, the capital of the bank reached 1.8 billion Birr in 2016. Its deposits in 2013/14 exceeded 16 billion birr. Wegagen Bank is a moderate sized bank with over 98 branches. Its headquarters are located at the new building that currently under construction in the central financial hub of Addis Ababa. It is one of 8 banks in Ethiopia that has launched a agent banking system.
